config:
  theme: neo
---
flowchart TD
    A([User activates Silent Mode]) --> B[Record timestamp and preferences]
    B --> C[Monitor incoming notifications]
    C --> D{Silent Mode active?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Receive new notification]
    D -->|No| I[Send notification immediately]
    E --> F{Priority level?}
    F -->|Critical or Emergency| G[Bypass queue]
    F -->|Normal or Low| H[Enter pending queue]
    G --> I
    H --> J["Mark as delayed, record timestamp"]
    J --> K{Silent mode ended?}
    K -->|No| C
    K -->|Yes or scheduled| L[Process queued notifications]
    L --> M[Group by category and priority]
    M --> N[Create structured summary]
    N --> O[Send batch response to user]
    I --> P([User receives response])
    O --> P

